### Psalms 82

[KJV](../kjv/psa082.md)

1  A Psalm<sup>[4210](h4210)</sup> of Asaph.<sup>[623](h0623.md)</sup>
God<sup>[430](h0430)</sup> standeth<sup>[5324](h5324.md)</sup> in the
congregation<sup>[5712](h5712.md)</sup> of the
mighty;<sup>[410](h0410)</sup> he judgeth<sup>[8199](h8199.md)</sup>
