2  How long<sup>[5704](h5704)</sup> <sup>[4970](h4970.md)</sup> will ye
judge<sup>[8199](h8199)</sup> unjustly,<sup>[5766](h5766.md)</sup> and
accept<sup>[5375](h5375)</sup> the persons<sup>[6440](h6440.md)</sup> of
