3  Defend<sup>[8199](h8199)</sup> the poor<sup>[1800](h1800.md)</sup> and
fatherless:<sup>[3490](h3490)</sup> do justice<sup>[6663](h6663.md)</sup>
to the afflicted<sup>[6041](h6041.md)</sup> and
needy.<sup>[7326](h7326.md)</sup>

4  Deliver<sup>[6403](h6403)</sup> the poor<sup>[1800](h1800.md)</sup> and
needy:<sup>[34](h0034)</sup> rid<sup>[5337](h5337.md)</sup> them out of the
hand<sup>[4480](h4480)</sup> <sup>[3027](h3027.md)</sup> of the
