5  They know<sup>[3045](h3045)</sup> not,<sup>[3808](h3808.md)</sup>
neither<sup>[3808](h3808.md)</sup> will they
understand;<sup>[995](h0995)</sup> they walk on<sup>[1980](h1980.md)</sup>
